message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.CL", "cs.IR", "cs.AI", "cs.LG", and "cs.CC". The paper discusses a new dataset and proposes a method for review-based question answering, which involves information retrieval and reading comprehension techniques. This task is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science, including natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and computational complexity (cs.CC).
